Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Light the fuse, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMEN]\NFire! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Henchmen]\NFire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Henchmen]\NFire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.39,0:02:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stabbing him in the back was\Na cowardly move, you Big Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Zoro?\NHow bad are you injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and don't\Nworry about how I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to concentrate if\NI'm gonna get us outta this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is... this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy, who's this?\NWho's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. She's\Nour new navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NMove...[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Desperate Situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast Tamer Mohji vs. Luffy."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess even a lowly pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...can still rescue his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] Those three\Nthink they can mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider this act of\Naggression a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NThere you are, Mohji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you wouldn't mind if\NI take the Pirate Hunter's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]\NBe my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Zoro]\NWhat's with this dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro, it looks like\Nthis dog is frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He could sit there\Nforever, for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOG barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--[DOG growling]\N--[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Get off!\NGet off! Get off! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, please, quit goofing\Naround and get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDamn dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI don't feel good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hi, navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me out of a\Npretty sticky situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! The key to the cage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go and\Nsteal if for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I only did it so we'd be even.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I don't owe you\Nanything. So we're square, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOG barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[DOG gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY growling]\N--[DOG howls]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NStupid, stupid, stupid, dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back. That's not food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me my key!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it, give it, give it, give\Nit, give it, give it, give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NHey! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop picking on poor Chouchou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might you be old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man? Why, I'm the\Nmayor of this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you and why are\Nyou hurting Chouchou? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my... that's quite an\Ninjury you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it that ya' had a\Nrun in with Captain Buggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get you to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him he really\Nshould see a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but he insisted that\Nhe didn't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and just wanted to sleep it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NSo this dog's name is Chouchou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he just\Nsitting there like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure is a lazy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's guarding the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's guarding it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I see. It's a pet food shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the man who\Nused to run this store
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,was a very close friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NThere ya' go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When he passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed the responsibility\Nof taking care of Chouchou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHe died?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,after fighting his illness\Nfor a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Don't tell me\Nhe's been waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for his master to\Nreturn all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NThat seems to be the consensus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I find that\Nvery hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouchou is a smart dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably known for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that his master\Nisn't coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... why does he\Nstay here at the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess because he has\Na connection to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his... treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's guarding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His master left\Nhim with this shop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why he protects it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried to bring\Nhim back to my place,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so he won't be out\Nin the elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but he won't take so much\Nas a step away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh? What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NIt's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast Tamer Mohji!\NWe gotta go! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] What do you mean\Nby "Beast Tamer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--[NAMI] Wait! Hold On!\N--[BOODLE] Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon puppy, something's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just\Ngive me that key back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LION GROWLING]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that your friends\Nhave deserted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And after you just escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWho the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm known as the\N"Beast Tamer Mohji,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a member of the Buggy Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, that's a weird\Nanimal suit you got on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LION roaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is manly hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,'K, That's even weirder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't assume that you're\Nsafe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,just because\Nyou're in that cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not know of\Nmy terrifying skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no animal\Nin this world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that Beast Tamer Mohji\Ncan't bend to do his bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,--[MOHJI screaming]\N--[CHOUCHOU growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it hurt so bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You nameless thief, I've\Nno interest in killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But tell me where\NRoronoa Zoro is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,before I change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Richie, Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[RICHIE roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NYes! I'm finally out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go find Zoro
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can defeat him and\Nstrengthen my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's, wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a pet food store.\NMake it quick, then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[RICHIE roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this\Npathetic little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,really thinks he\Ncan guard the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhew, that was intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now, I'm\Nout of that cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHe.He.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, first thing, I teach\Nthose Buggy Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a lesson and then\NI convince Nami
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to be the navigator for my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you survive that attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got lucky, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Surviving an attack\Nlike that isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd be\Nscattered all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NIt's not normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why exactly did you decide\Nto come to this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and how'd you get involved\Nwith those pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'm doing is searching\Nfor a chart of the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and a good navigator\Nto join my pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I think that\Nguy in the animal suit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,said he was looking for\NZoro, so, I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[RICHIE ROARING]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[OWNER] Chouchou? This shop\Nbelongs to the two of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. Ha. That bag is way\Ntoo big for you, Chouchou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[RICHIE growls]\N[CHOUCHOU snarling]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[OWNER grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[OWNER laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Chouchou.\NDon't hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[OWNER]\NHmm. Bad Chouchou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to\Neat the merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's chow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:12:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU, RICHIE growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Not ready\Nto give up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[OWNER] Chouchou, I'm\Ngetting on in years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go see the\Ndoctor for a checkup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll be back, so guard\Nthe shop until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Chouchou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold down the fort!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU, RICHIE growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[OWNER laughs]\NThat tickles, Chouchou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NHe has a connection to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's guarding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,His master left\Nhim with this shop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why he protects it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[howls, barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[barks, howls]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI]\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that\Nannoying little dog bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I thought I killed you.\NWhat are you still doing alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you can't get\Nrid of me that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This time crush his head\Ninto the ground, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[RICHIE roars]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna be\Nbeaten by a lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI]\NWhat are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I ate the\NGum-Gum Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI gasps]\NSo then you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...Devil Fruit powers\Nlike Captain Buggy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but yours make you rubber?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I apologize\Nfor attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] There's no reason\Nfor you to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of you, that dog will\Nnever get his treasure back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... because of that,\NI'm gonna kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI whimpers, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY yells]\N--[MOHJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all just a bunch\Nof heartless bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They destroy everything\Nthat people hold dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,without giving it\Na second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're alive, Pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I thought\Nfor sure that lion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,was gonna tear your\Nhead off and end it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wish he had,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause then there'd be one\Nless pirate in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should\Nkill you right now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,before you can gather a crew
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy everything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NCome now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no need for violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAs if you could ever kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NWell, maybe I'll try it and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NI said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but that's all\Nthat I could save for ya'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard lion ate\Nall the rest of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He fought the lion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...in order to save\Nthe dog's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou fought well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Course I didn't actually\Nsee you defend the store,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can tell you\Ngave it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[CHOUCHOU barks]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck to you, too, doggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[barking]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NYou were defeated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm very sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mohji, I can't believe you\Nwere defeated by Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that straw hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that\Nskinny little punk
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,could have gotten\Nthe better of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[MOHJI]\NHe's eaten the Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm really pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Prepare all the\Nremaining Special Buggy Balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna blow this entire,\Nmiserable town to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NSorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to yell at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, you've been\Nunder a lot of stress lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chouchou and this young\None have fought so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet I, the mayor, have done\Nnothing but sit back and watch
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,our town be obliterated by\NBuggy and his despicable crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! It's not that bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,this whole area was nothing\Nbut barren, rugged land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We all worked together to\Ncreate fields for our crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We opened stores, and built\Neverything from the ground up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This town is a treasure\Nto me and all its citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to let Buggy and his\Ncrew terrorize us any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY]\NFire a Special Buggy Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow this town away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll destroy it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Zoro was sleeping in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NI'm sure he's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NZoro, you in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] That's one hell of\Na way to wake a guy up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:20:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI coulda used a few more z's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you survive that blast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE] I refuse to let\Nhim get away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let this\Nscumbag destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all that my townspeople worked\Nfor these last forty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NI am the mayor of this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect it\Nand it's inhabitants!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear... to my dying breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NStop! You can't defeat Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NPerhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there are some fights\Nthat a man can't run from!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't egg\Nhim on, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous for\Nhim to fight Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE] I'm coming for\Nyou, Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThe mayor was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHe was? Huh, I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Looks like the\Nparty's getting more exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]\NSure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I started to\Ngrow fond of that old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWell, In that case ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the injury to my reputation's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot worse than the\Ninjury to my gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we want to get\Nto the Grand Line....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...we better go steal\Nthat chart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Are you gonna\Njoin our crew or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never sink so low\Nas to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I suppose we\Ncould team up,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to achieve\Nour common goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[HENCHMAN J]\NThe second shot is ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE]\NCome out, Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mayor Boodle and this\Ntown is my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you terrorize\Nmy people any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so come out and fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! This town\Nis no treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure is gold,\Nsilver, and jewelry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So cut the crap, old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and get outta here\Nbefore I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You could never\Nunderstand how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY] Soon I'm going to\Nconquer the Grand Line and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,flashily obtain all\Nthe world's riches,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nothing\Nyou can do to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All the world will belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if this town\Nmeans so much to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,then perhaps I'll do you a\Nfavor and kill you first,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that way you won't\Nhave to see me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,destroy your precious village.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOODLE grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up... and fight me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.69,0:22:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let you\Ndestroy this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if it costs me my very life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[BUGGY laughs]\NSo be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That straw hat! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to kick your ass, just\Nlike I promised I would, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.60,0:23:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.70,0:23:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:24:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.15,0:24:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.24,0:24:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.71,0:24:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.34,0:24:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have to take on\None of their swordsmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.51,0:24:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI'll clash swords with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAre you sure? You're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.76,0:24:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Huh. I'll show you\Nhow superior my skills are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.39,0:24:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOoh! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.97,0:24:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] My ambition is to be\Nthe world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.39,0:24:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to\Nlose to anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.98,0:24:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,who calls himself\Na swordfighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.69,0:24:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.36,0:24:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Epic Showdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.61,0:24:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Swordsman Zoro\Nvs. Acrobat Cabaji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.40,0:24:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

